.row
  .col-md-8
    %div
      -# %h2 About
      %p
        Weld is the reference implementation of
        %a{:href=>"http://cdi-spec.org",:target=>'_blank'} CDI: Contexts and Dependency Injection for the Java EE Platform
        which is a
        %a{:href=>"https://jcp.org/en/home/index",:target=>'_blank'} JCP
        standard for dependency injection and contextual lifecycle management and one of the most important and popular parts of the Java EE platform.
      %p
        Weld is integrated into many Java EE application servers such as
        = succeed ',' do
          %a{:href=>"http://www.wildfly.org/",:target=>'_blank'}WildFly
        = succeed ',' do
          %a{:href=>"http://www.jboss.org/products/eap.html",:target=>'_blank'}JBoss Enterprise Application Platform
        = succeed ',' do
          %a{:href=>"http://glassfish.java.net/",:target=>'_blank'}GlassFish
        = succeed ',' do
          %a{:href=>"http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/middleware/weblogic/overview/index.html",:target=>'_blank'}Oracle WebLogic Server
        %a{:href=>"https://developer.ibm.com/wasdev/downloads/",:target=>'_blank'}WebSphere Application Server
        and others. Weld can also be used in a
        %a{:href=>"http://docs.jboss.org/weld/reference/latest-master/en-US/html/environments.html#weld-servlet",:target=>'_blank'}Servlet-only environment (Tomcat, Jetty)
        or plain
        %a{:href=>"http://docs.jboss.org/weld/reference/latest-master/en-US/html/environments.html#weld-se",:target=>'_blank'}Java SE environment.
      %h2 Try Weld Today
      %div
        %p
          To use Weld today, download the
          %a{:href=>"http://wildfly.org",:target=>'_blank'}WildFly server
          (formerly JBoss AS) and add the following code to the
          %code pom.xml
          file of your application:
        %pre.code
          %code.xml
            = preserve do
              :escaped
                <dependency>
                   <groupId>javax.enterprise</groupId>
                   <artifactId>cdi-api</artifactId>
                   <version>1.2</version>
                   <scope>provided</scope>
                </dependency>
        %p
          For alternative ways of using Weld, see the
          %a{:href=>"/download"}download section
          or the
          %a{:href=>"http://docs.jboss.org/weld/reference/latest/en-US/html/environments.html"}reference documentation.
      %div
        %h2 Weld Book
        %p The latest book on Weld is now available:
        %div#book-box
          %a{:href=>"http://www.packtpub.com/jboss-weld-cdi-for-java-platform/book"}
            %img{:src=>"images/book.jpg", :width=>"250", :height=>"307", :class=>"weld-book-img"}
  .col-md-1
    %div
  .col-md-4
    %div.well
      %h2
        Latest News
        %a{:href=>"http://weld.cdi-spec.org/news.atom"}
          %i.fa.fa-rss
      %hr
      %ul.newsColumn
        - for post in site.posts[0,5]
          %li
            %h3
              %a{ :href=>post.url }#{post.title}
            - if (post.content.length > 0)
              %div.news-date.news-boxed
                #{post.date.year}-#{post.date.month}-#{post.date.day}
              %p
                = post.excerpt || summarize(html_to_text(post.content), 20)
                %a{:href=>post.url} more
              %hr
